					Full Description



		Mobile Telecommunications Limited is a global outsourcing, manufacturing and consulting company catering to a host of industries and sectors. The Company's principal business activities include electronic appliances, electronic hardware, networking equipment, power bank, telecom equipment and embedded software. Its offerings include business process outsourcing (BPO) services, wireless communication and software development. It supplies point of sale (PoS) systems, electronic cables, retail PoS systems, speakers and home theater systems, and light-emitting diode products. Its product range includes analog cables (molded), solar cables, control cables, submersible cables and heat resistant cables. It offers a range of printed circuit breakers (PCBs) from double-sided to multi-layers, high density interconnection (HDI), and material and processes. It offers card readers and encoders for baking use, e-cash register for hospitality and retail, and all-in-one PoS terminals, among others.
» Full Overview of MOBI.BO







