Our past, present, and future
''We help companies create the paths to their goals''

Mobile Telecommunications Ltd. – popularly called Mobiletele or MTL – a global outsourcing, manufacturing, and consulting company catering to a host of industries and sectors. Incorporated in 1995, we are headquartered in Mumbai, India, and have offices in Nashik, India, and New York and New Jersey, US. We are also publicly listed on the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE). Employing over 1000 people across our locations, Mobiletele posted an annual turnover of. 
